{"pid":"57892613cb1d40402682d0fbbf19264604df0364","tid":1701862,"uid":157275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841f6134b7167afca4b491e5162f0445c1fb34b1","tid":1701862,"uid":132106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:01:33.000Z","msg":"裝修啦 講閪咩"},{"pid":"09a2cbd720d2192a5f0785a7301524da6edcaf75","tid":1701862,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"有冇腦架，罷工前炒人咪盞仲多人出黎罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad92d812a9b310a9f4d7a179452ba8c0b7ed97ca","tid":1701862,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"仲未入藍店名單WOR<br />\n相信要盡快UPDATE"},{"pid":"c9fbbf0e8e83d4cc1745a3325baee607e6222caf","tid":1701862,"uid":276670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21bbc4e5c4eb409c7a072328f4a37d9607c17b84","tid":1701862,"uid":157275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"【本網訊】香港廚師聯盟工會主席吳志輝（細輝），原本任職位於香港紗廠的將軍堡餐廳，今日傳出被炒消息，仲要簽保密協議。未罷工先炒工會主席，如同代政權出手嚇工友。<br />\n<br />\n細輝接受&laquo;基進報導&raquo;訪問時透露，星期二在廚房大佬口中得知，公司以生意不好為由，需要調整營業時間削減人手開支，最初說考慮解僱另一位資歷較淺的廚師。後來星期五時，突然他引述公司指，因為「有很多報導、身份敏感」為由，公司希望將細輝辭退。<br />\n<br />\n將軍堡餐廳昨晚與細輝處理好合約內的金錢和薪金，又要求他簽下保密協議。細輝指，自己是在脅迫下簽名，「你說，這樣有沒有法律效力？」<br />\n<br />\n細輝除了是工會主席，亦是8.31事件現場目擊者之一，多次公開講述當晚情況。對於公司在三罷前解僱自己，他認為是出於政治打壓。細輝自己在3月在招聘廣告一般途徑入職，雖然廚房大佬亦說希望留用自己，但公司和母公司「新匯江」本身「藍底」，其他餐廳亦會受制於警方不敢聘用他，憂慮未能找到其他工作：「後面還會很多人會給餐廳壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n在科大生被警方逼死後，香港市民正打算發動全面三罷抗爭，當中組工會更是不少群組的首要議程。今次餐廳先幫政權出手打壓，既是打壓工人，更是對三罷運動全面宣戰。<br />\n<br />\n@香港廚師聯盟<br />\n<br />\n（持咪者為吳志輝，資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://radicalhk.com/2019/11/09/fire-chef/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fradicalhk.com%2F2019%2F11%2F09%2Ffire-chef%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=c9dd2225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://radicalhk.com/2019/11/09/fire-chef/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"工員主席唔一定要「現職員工」<br />\n可以搵個非員工代工會出聲<br />\n<br />\n解決炒主席之問題"},{"pid":"bb56655adc3230c97efdaf2fad0f6810acdad133","tid":1701862,"uid":157275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"推比多D人睇 果頭咁多工廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcbe79d78355b1525b8db32ce8fad115c5d2eb4","tid":1701862,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇咗原來被解僱廚師係觀塘區參選人<br />\n依家唔應該做任何野 費事話選舉不公平"},{"pid":"2fb6ce7ee2f6e73536ea31b5b197115e44ee30cf","tid":1701862,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"吉野家都裝修黎講<br />\n呢間點會係列表之外？"},{"pid":"259ca16d4606b38f22bb13961d3f4d4301561808","tid":1701862,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a59e634e11ad32f039545eb3f36a1cb2690b97","tid":1701862,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"罷食足矣"},{"pid":"e0112cdd1f41cdd522b7f555bb565f5534b05e6c","tid":1701862,"uid":157275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bb4b432c653422468c4cfdf28b67ae95930561","tid":1701862,"uid":1712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:30:47.000Z","msg":"劉小麗啲fd黎<br />\n之前劉小麗俾人屌佢捐人工單野唔夠數<br />\n佢即刻補返捐10萬入呢個聯